target":"recLuZtSmAO6erIsc","label":"mentions"},{"source":"reczBad36lQl4gx3F","target":"recxvUZPfI3eUQddE","label":"mentions"},{"source":"reczBad36lQl4gx3F","target":"reccZB8SVU5bEMcgo","label":"mentions"},{"source":"reczBad36lQl4gx3F","target":"recYI8GwhUiwlzWZu","label":"mentions"},{"source":"reczBad36lQl4gx3F","target":"recRIRFGthibBMRBt","label":"mentions"},{"source":"reczBad36lQl4gx3F","target":"recU2yIahYCFP7hLG","label":"mentions"},{"source":"reczBad36lQl4gx3F","target":"rec3gWYVMktOUkAzZ","label":"mentions"},{"source":"reczBad36lQl4gx3F","target":"recLcxRZbz3yIQB7b","label":"mentions"},{"source":"reczBad36lQl4gx3F","target":"recN4jruK7QVakoJh","label":"mentions"},{"source":"reczBad36lQl4gx3F","target":"recMFUSc6GzrLNNtt","label":"mentions"},{"source":"reczBad36lQl4gx3F","target":"rec72wlsoWnXTzVfy","label":"mentions"},{"source":"reczBad36lQl4gx3F","target":"recL1WV82pXaRBQ59","label":"mentions"},{"source":"reczBad36lQl4gx3F","target":"recVYcDguYN6bVqxy","label":"mentions"},{"source":"reczBad36lQl4gx3F","target":"recmzFZzjfqsRjkZ9","label":"mentions"},{"source":"reczBad36lQl4gx3F","target":"recn47IzNNlhvTtXK","label":"mentions"},{"source":"reczBad36lQl4gx3F","target":"recJSfVnIcPibY6aX","label":"mentions"}],"verses":[{"id":"recegIhQcNlt9xm6J","ref":"Josh.15.1","text":"This then was the lot of the tribe of the children of Judah by their families; even to the border of Edom the wilderness of Zin southward was the uttermost part of the south coast.","year":-1443},{"id":"recJsriT5J0Xs7gJJ","ref":"Josh.15.2","text":"And their south border was from the shore of the salt sea, from the bay that looketh southward:","year":-1443},{"id":"recxX7bnbcMw3Y0MQ","ref":"Josh.15.3","text":"And it went out to the south side to Maalehacrabbim, and passed along to Zin, and ascended up on the south side unto Kadeshbarnea, and passed along to Hezron, and went up to Adar, and fetched a compass to Karkaa:","year":-1443},{"id":"rectvvlsUAP1NKPyG","ref":"Josh.15.4","text":"From thence it passed toward Azmon, and went out unto the river of Egypt; and the goings out of that coast were at the sea: this shall be your south coast.","year":-1443},{"id":"recH9ISjG99M437yL","ref":"Josh.15.5","text":"And the east border was the salt sea, even unto the end of Jordan. And their border in the north quarter was from the bay of the sea at the uttermost part of Jordan:","year":-1443},{"id":"rec9aNNQ4Dl34uKKB","ref":"Josh.15.6","text":"And the border went up to Bethhogla, and passed along by the north of Betharabah; and the border went up to the stone of Bohan the son of Reuben:","year":-1443},{"id":"recQfD1TLuyT0ydRx","ref":"Josh.15.7","text":"And the border went up toward Debir from the valley of Achor, and so northward, looking toward Gilgal, that is before the going up to Adummim, which is on the south side of the river: and the border passed toward the waters of Enshemesh, and the goings out thereof were at Enrogel:","year":-1443},{"id":"recvE0mDwEFlBHPCC","ref":"Josh.15.8","text":"And the border went up by the valley of the son of Hinnom unto the south side of the Jebusite; the same is Jerusalem: and the border went up to the top of the mountain that lieth before the valley of Hinnom westward, which is at the end of the valley of the giants northward:","year":-1443}]}
